\fs50 24 whole Oreo cookies\uc0\u8232 1/4 cup melted unsalted butter\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\ql\qnatural

\fs56 \cf0 \uc0\u8232 
\b\fs50 Preparation:
\b0\fs56 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa260\ql\qnatural

\fs50 \cf0 In a medium-sized bowl or a food processor, add the Oreo cookies and blend until the texture of coarse meal. Add the melted butter and blend until well combined.\
Place the ground crumb mixture into a 9- or 10-inch springform pan and press onto the bottom and up the sides evenly. Refrigerate the crust for at least an hour before you add the filling of your choice. \cf3 This will help prevent crumbling when you want to serve it.\cf0 \
